snippet.title: Airaki (GameBoy Color) demo gameplay
snippet.description: Preview of FSE's new GameBoy title: a small puzzle-RPG named Airaki. Interested ? Get your copy here: http://furrtek.free.fr/fse/?p=airakien ... Or wait for someone to dump the ROM ;)
